query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathematica')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('bugs',
'calculus-and-analysis',
'differential-equations',
'equation-solving',
'functions',
'graphics',
'graphics3d',
'list-manipulation',
'numerical-integration',
'numerics',
'plotting');
